# Module Dependency Map

This is one of the most important diagrams in the project.

```text
Authentication
        │
        ▼
Users
        │
        ▼
Addresses
        │
        ▼
Cart
        │
        ▼
Checkout
        │
        ▼
Payments
        │
        ▼
Orders
        │
        ▼
Shipping
        │
        ▼
Reviews
```

Notice something?

Every module depends on the previous one.

You cannot build **Orders** before **Payments**.

You cannot build **Payments** before **Checkout**.

You cannot build **Checkout** before **Cart**.

This dependency map becomes your implementation order.

