# Real Production Database Modules

If this project grows into a large platform, each area can become its own service.

```
Authentication Service

User Service

Product Service

Inventory Service

Cart Service

Order Service

Payment Service

Notification Service

Analytics Service
```

We won't build microservices now, but designing with these boundaries makes future growth easier.

