# Phase Completion Checklist

Before we create any SQL tables, make sure you can answer **yes** to all of these:

* [ ] I know every actor (Guest, Customer, Admin).
* [ ] I know every business module.
* [ ] I know how modules depend on each other.
* [ ] I know the customer's journey.
* [ ] I know the important business events.
* [ ] I have a folder ready for database design.
* [ ] I have documented the naming conventions.

If any answer is "No", stop and complete it before moving on.

